Workshop dinner

The workshop dinner can be attended on Thursday 25th April. Payment is the responsibility of the participant.

The dinner will be held at Club Nàutic. The Nautical Club, the second oldest in the Illes Balears after the one in Ciutadella (Menorca), was founded on February 27, 1925 by a group of enthusiastic sea fans led by Don Francisco Costa Torres, the first president of the club.
